West Bengal
Sep 17, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			Police have arrested local vegetable vendors Zakir Hussain, Akthar Mollah, Surajit Chowdhury all residents of Jinjira Bazar for raping the girl. The victim said she was sleeping on the station complex as it was very hot in the evening. Four youths dragged her to a nearby place and took turns in raping her when she was going to toilet. She could not even raise an alarm as they gagged her. Police are looking for the fourth person involved in the act.
